rComments: Sundhya is one of the most exquisite creatures ever to have graced English Dept halls...  Kind, brilliant, beautiful. TAKE HER CLASSES. She is quietly captivating.

Sundhya was intelligent, kind and organized. The theories could be quite dense but she did a wonderful job of explaining and illustrating them through examples from both literary and non-literary texts. Sometimes she would also apply the theorists' ideas to analyze contemporary events, making us the relevance and importance of what we were learning
